name: Not a How To
body:
I tried to get Jekyll running on my laptop, I really did.  But didn't.

Here are some links to my ever growing list of pertinent missives.  If you were a programmer, you would know that even if there were no links below, it would still be a list.

***
   
###[Adjusting to C  - Oct 21, 2013](http://tspurway.github.io/adjusting_to_c.html)
A cheeky look at malloc() from a programmer who should know better
